high_descs: Move to the table, the side of the table with no chair.
Pick up the knife from the right side near the spoon.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the toaster.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Turn left, move to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the knife on to the plate.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the toaster.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left, move to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the potato slice on to the plate.
Pick up the plate with the potato slice and knife on it.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the plate onto a low shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of potato onto a place, place the plate in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Move forward, then right, and face the round table on your left.
Pick up the knife on the table in front of you.
Turn left and head towards the counter with the lettuce on it.
Slice the potato on the counter by the toaster.
Turn around then head towards the counter by the stove to your right.
Place the knife on the plate on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter with the lettuce on your left.
Take a potato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn around then head towards the counter by the stove on your right.
Place the potato slice on the plate on the counter in front of you.
Take the plate with the potato and knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and head towards the fridge in front of you.
Place the plate with the potato and knife in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a potato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward, turn right when the counter at the right ends, go forward to the wall, turn left to the round white table.
Take the knife on the right of the table.
Turn left, go forward and to the left to the counter to the right of the sink.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn left, go forward and to the left to the counter to the right of the oven.
Put the knife on the apple on the counter.
Turn around, go back to the counter to the right of the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left, go forward and to the left to the counter to the right of the oven.
Put the potato on the white plate on the counter.
Take the plate from the counter.
Turn right, go forward to the fridge.
Put the plate on the rack in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a potato slice on it in a fridge.

high_descs: turn right, then look left to face the table
pick up the knife on the table
go to the other side of the room and face the toaster
slice the potato in front of the toaster
go straight to the counter top on the opposite side, then turn right until you reach the stove top
place the knife on the counter top over the apple
return to the counter top with the toaster
pick up a slice of potato from the counter top
return to the counter top with the stove top
place the potato slice on the plate to the right of the stove top
pick up the plate on the counter top
turn right and go to the refrigerator
open the door and place the plate on the bottom shelf
anns.task_desc: slice a potato and plate it to cool it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Walk across the room, turn right, and walk to the table.
Pick up a knife from the table.
Turn left and walk to the counter with lettuce and a potato.
Slice half of the potato.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the counter with an apple and a white plate.
Set the knife down on a plate on the table.
Turn around and walk across the room to the counter with the potato on the left.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and walk across the room, turn right to the counter with the plate and knife.
Set the potato slice on the plate with the knife.
Pick up the plate with the knife and potato slice.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and set the slice with the potato slice inside, close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a potato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go to the white round table on the other side of the kitchen.
Pick up the paring knife on the table.
Turn to left to go to the kitchen counter with a potato on top.
Slice the potato on the table.
Turn around and go to the kitchen counter next to the stove on the right.
Place the paring knife on the white plate.
Turn around and go back to the kitchen counter with the sliced potato.
Pick up one slice of potato.
Go back to the kitchen counter next to the stove.
Place the slice of potato on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the slice of potato and paring knife on it.
Turn around and go to left to the refrigerator.
Place the plate with potato and knife in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of potato and the knife on the plate in the fridge.
